 Linkin Park 吉他手 Brad Delson 确认他将缺席所有现场表演https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-guitarist-brad-delson-confirms-he-will-sit-out-of-all-live-shows-3791566?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=林肯公园吉他手布拉德·德尔森确认他将缺席所有现场表演Laura MolloySat, 07 Sep 2024 08:06:22 +0000 Music NewsNewsNu-metalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3791566 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他确认将继续与乐队在幕后合作</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-guitarist-brad-delson-confirms-he-will-sit-out-of-all-live-shows-3791566">Linkin Park 后吉他手 Brad Delson 确认他将缺席所有</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的现场表演。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Brad-Delson.-CREDIT_-Francesco-Castaldo_Archivio-Francesco-Castaldo_Mondadori-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park" target="_blank" rel="noopener">林肯公园 (Linkin Park)</a>的吉他手布拉德·德尔森 (Brad Delson) 宣布他不会参加乐队即将举行的世界巡演。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/linkin-park-new-singer-emily-armstrong-chester-bennington-from-zero-3791172">“这不是结束，这不是开始”：林肯公园以新面孔展望未来</a></strong></li></ul><p>本周早些时候，Linkin Park <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-announce-new-singer-album-and-world-tour-3791116">通过直播活动宣布回归</a>，并透露在阵容中增加了两名新成员：前 Dead Sara 乐队主唱 Emily Armstrong 和鼓手 Colin Brittain。</p><p>他们表演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-linkin-park-played-at-their-comeback-gig-3791136">一首新歌《The Emptiness Machine》和几首 Linkin Park 经典歌曲</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-announce-new-singer-album-and-world-tour-3791116">宣布推出新专辑《From Zero》，并在全球进行了六场简短的支持世界巡演</a>。这是自<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/chester-bennington-obituary-1976-2017-2113700">2017 年查斯特·贝宁顿去世</a>以来他们的第一首新音乐。</p><p>在与<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/rock/linkin-park-singer-tour-album-cover-story-interview-1235766805/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard</em></a>谈论他们的复出时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mike-shinoda">Mike Shinoda</a>指出， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-address-founding-drummer-rob-bourdons-departure-3791129">乐队创始成员之一的鼓手 Rob Bourdon 已决定离开乐队</a>。</p><p>现在，创始吉他手布拉德·德尔森表示，他也不会参加乐队即将举行的世界巡演，但将继续与他们进行幕后合作，包括参与新音乐的创作。</p><p>昨晚（9 月 6 日）在 Instagram 上发布的一份声明中，德尔森感谢粉丝们的“支持和喜爱”，并表示他“敬畏”新成员阿姆斯特朗和布里顿“的才华、热情和合作关系”。</p><p> “我一直对我们的现场表演有着深深的感情，并为之感到自豪。多年来，我意识到当我在幕后积极与乐队成员合作时，我才能最茁壮成长——在录音室里，合作创作我们的新音乐，并帮助打造我们的现场表演，”他说。</p><p>德尔森还透露，在本周的直播活动中加入 Linkin Park 的吉他手亚历克斯·费德 (Alex Feder) 将在乐队未来的现场表演中扮演自己的角色。</p><p> “我对我们继续共同创造的一切感到非常自豪。虽然我不会在这个新篇章中进行巡演，但我非常兴奋地介绍亚历克斯——我在路上的英俊副手。 Alex 是一位世界级的音乐家，一位善良而体贴的朋友，我们真的很幸运，他将为我们的唱片世界贡献他独特的才华。</p><p> “新鲜的眼光、真诚的欣赏和专注的团队合作让我们迎来了这个特殊的时刻。很荣幸与您分享我们的创造力。感谢您加入我们的旅程。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_lurY4Sglx/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" backgro